{"tid":1963609,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"弱弩之末 - 李碧華","createTime":"2020-04-08T08:58:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-08T08:58:41.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"07b79996872e3f56fccdc3d9c9c8b9afd837dff5","tid":1963609,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T08:58:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E6%9D%8E%E7%A2%A7%E8%8F%AF/daily/article/20200408/20895793/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E6%259D%258E%25E7%25A2%25A7%25E8%258F%25AF%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200408%2F20895793%2F&d=LgTIxyFtuo0acoW68XVTBb%2BiaDmtBxIfZa%2Bp1tlHcc8%3D&h=54c6a6df\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E6%259D%258E%25E7%25A2%25A7%25E8%258F%25AF%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200408%2F20895793%2F&h=81122b46\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E6%9D%8E%E7%A2%A7%E8%8F%AF/daily/article/20200408/20895793/</a><br />\n<br />\n弱弩之末 - 李碧華<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20200408/large/1586242409_ae8e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20200408%2Flarge%2F1586242409_ae8e.jpg&h=6c42c1cd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n報導指立法會議員容海恩，到警察總部報案，檢舉一個社交網站專頁「香港黑警」，內容煽動暴力及仇警，希望警方深入調查，云云。<br />\n<br />\n容以「西環契女」人事關係，投葉劉新民黨催谷上位，非憑實力、民意、功績，雖貌似馬海倫（桂綸鎂？想創你個心！），「明星相」無補於事，向以天真、無知見著。奉子成婚，「一年抱兩」，丈夫傾向民主派，常發言表態，與容政見不合。<br />\n<br />\n建制派宮女公公，立會中尸位素餐又豈止一兩人？皆舉手機器，吃公帑毋須多餘動作，除非要刷存在感。<br />\n<br />\n容到了近日才動作頻仍還去撐警舉報網站，又一天真、無知明證──黑警資料肯定瞭如指掌，還待人提醒？只因容面臨衞生巾避孕套命運，被西環一腳踢開，以背（自由）黨過底之西門梓敬取代參選，葉劉也沒力保，人情冷暖世態炎涼，40多了，還不明白嗎？「議會內外都不應該牽涉太多政治」？昨天才出生嗎？<br />\n<br />\n想當年，自己也被「內定」盲推，怎能看不過其他人被「內定」？每支箭都有射程，有衰竭的一天，何況並非出於「強弩」──弱弩之末別費勁，回家帶孩子（兩女）也罷，強調教她倆任何顏色偏不教「黃色」？愚忠色盲會誤了後代。世間父母，到底也應為子女着想的。 <br />\n<br />\n李碧華<br />\n電郵 :mcwriter@appledaily.com"},{"pid":"275c08b315e2f682f314f2719285af05ddb62694","tid":1963609,"uid":157799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T08:58:41.000Z","msg":"唔好意思，好怕大家忘記了，可唔可以入嚟幫手推一推<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n［5個月］［整合］大家記唔記得今日係咩日子<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1963297\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1963297</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/04/08/163118_9b725230f319dbfd347dc84fa175d02e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F04%2F08%2F163118_9b725230f319dbfd347dc84fa175d02e.png&h=4188adbd&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}